'max_depth'","position":{"start":{"line":169,"column":1},"end":{"line":169,"column":1}},"key":"f5P0lHD7UW"},{"type":"text","value":" des Entscheidungsbaums justiert werden. Wie zuvor in der\nfor-Schleife, untersuchen wir die Baumtiefen 3, 4, 5 und 6, die im folgenden\nDictionary ","position":{"start":{"line":169,"column":1},"end":{"line":169,"column":1}},"key":"VdY1naV9iV"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"parameter_gitter","position":{"start":{"line":169,"column":1},"end":{"line":169,"column":1}},"key":"po57mNVE73"},{"type":"text","value":" definiert werden.","position":{"start":{"line":169,"column":1},"end":{"line":169,"column":1}},"key":"kkNZqeYw0p"}],"key":"s0p6hsot79"}],"key":"CsSZr0ScPS"},{"type":"block","kind":"notebook-code","children":[{"type":"code","lang":"python","executable":true,"value":"from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV\n\n# Festlegung des Suchraumes\nparameter_gitter = {'max_depth': [3, 4, 5, 6]}","key":"HiWwn5ZLiS"},{"type":"outputs","id":"0DpP2kiFPNh6vJEpuvk0Z","children":[],"key":"PIV4kbDtzc"}],"key":"TiVdFs0PGC"},{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":185,"column":1},"end":{"line":191,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nun instanziieren wir ein neues ","position":{"start":{"line":185,"column":1},"end":{"line":185,"column":1}},"key":"AgIAZ9ghdv"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"GridSearchCV","position":{"start":{"line":185,"column":1},"end":{"line":185,"column":1}},"key":"seV7zYeZgk"},{"type":"text","value":"-Modell. Als erstes Argument\nübergeben wir das eigentliche Modell, hier also den Entscheidungsbaum, und als\nzweites das Dictionary mit den Hyperparametern. Das dritte Argument ist die\nMethode zur Kreuzvalidierung. Weitere Details können Sie der ","position":{"start":{"line":185,"column":1},"end":{"line":185,"column":1}},"key":"G0sP5iOIfn"},{"type":"link","url":"https://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/generated/sklearn.model_selection.GridSearchCV.html#sklearn.model_selection.GridS